This is Pac North IC
requesting SPD Bomb Squad,

18:48.752 --> 18:50.128
Code Red response.

18:50.128 --> 18:51.838
And we still have a news chopper
and a drone.

18:51.838 --> 18:52.839
Medevac's still not clear
to land.

18:52.839 --> 18:54.549
There's my girl.

18:54.549 --> 18:57.177
Being boss.

18:57.177 --> 18:58.470
Dad, what are you
doing here?

18:58.470 --> 19:00.096
Well, I saw you
on the news.

