19:02.098 --> 19:03.808
Dad, you can't ‐‐
Don't "Dad" me.

19:03.808 --> 19:05.936
Go do something,
Captain.

19:05.936 --> 19:07.437
Go.

19:12.359 --> 19:14.069
you got to stay awake
for us, okay?

