And if it is a pattern,
that bomb will go off

19:54.109 --> 19:56.152
in elev‐‐
11 minutes.

19:56.152 --> 19:58.905
Stop. Stop it.

19:58.905 --> 20:01.074
Go help ‐‐
Go help him.

20:01.074 --> 20:02.909
Get my life's work
