20:06.705 --> 20:08.957
Save my life's work.

20:08.957 --> 20:12.252
Save ‐‐
Save countless millions.

20:12.252 --> 20:13.295
Please!

20:13.295 --> 20:14.796
Go.

20:17.132 --> 20:18.758
 Okay.

20:20.510 --> 20:21.678
Ready?

20:21.678 --> 20:23.054
Ready.

