25:49.422 --> 25:51.007
Autoclave.

25:51.007 --> 25:53.301
Over there.
It looks like a microwave.

25:53.301 --> 25:54.260
 Right.
Right, right, right, right.

25:54.260 --> 25:56.220
It's for sterilization,
but it's airtight.

25:56.220 --> 25:58.598
It can dampen
the explosion.

25:58.598 --> 25:59.891
We got to get it
closer to the bomb.

26:01.392 --> 26:03.353
It's ‐‐ It's ‐‐
It's bolted down.

26:05.647 --> 26:07.607
Dad, interfering with
