26:16.157 --> 26:18.201
Get your hands
off of me!

26:24.248 --> 26:25.375
This thing's
not going anywhere.

26:25.375 --> 26:27.043
And we are
running out of time.

26:27.043 --> 26:28.753
Four minutes.
Four minutes!

26:32.006 --> 26:33.800
 Whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa!
 Miller! Miller!

26:33.800 --> 26:35.593
No, no,
guys, guys, guys!

26:35.593 --> 26:37.178
Either I put that in there
or we all die.

26:37.178 --> 26:39.639
And my research.
Please.

26:39.639 --> 26:41.099
Countless millions,
right?

26:41.099 --> 26:41.891
Yeah.

26:45.478 --> 26:47.355
Let me do it.
No. No.

26:47.355 --> 26:48.690
Hey, hey.

26:48.690 --> 26:50.233
I'm not gonna let you
orphan your daughter.

26:50.233 --> 26:51.985
I'm not letting you ‐‐ No!
Let me do ‐‐ Let me do it!

26:54.445 --> 26:55.780
Oh, yeah.

26:55.780 --> 26:58.116
Oh, you need your big, strong
men to fight your battles,

26:58.116 --> 27:00.326
huh, Captain?
No, Dad, I don't!

27:00.326 --> 27:02.161
I don't need to
win my gold medals
through other people.

27:02.161 --> 27:04.664
Unlike you,
I win them myself.

27:07.500 --> 27:09.877
I'm fine.
Everyone back to work.

27:09.877 --> 27:11.546
Go on. Get to
the other side. Let's go.

27:11.546 --> 27:12.547
I'm gonna open the door.
Come on.

27:12.547 --> 27:13.673
To the other side!
Let's go!

27:13.673 --> 27:15.633
Go, go, go!
That's an order. Let's go!

27:17.385 --> 27:18.886
Dr. Alba?
 Other side now.

27:18.886 --> 27:20.680
That's an order.
To the other side.
Dr. Alba?

27:20.680 --> 27:22.014
Dr. Alba, we're gonna
move you now, okay?

27:22.014 --> 27:23.474
She's gone.

27:23.474 --> 27:25.393
She's gone.

